  <thing id="wpT2KM16APMine" name="M16 Anti-Personnel Mine" description="The M16 is a bounding mine with only three small vertical prongs showing above ground. When these are stepped off (after being stepped on), or their tripwire is pulled, the 2.5 kg mine flies 0.5 to 1.5 meters in the air and explodes. The airburst prevents  dropping prone from having a beneficial effect on avoiding wounds.  Several other countries also make copies of this mine, which makes it harder to identify when used." compset="Heavy">
