  <thing id="wpT2KM18Claymore" name="M18 Claymore Mine" description="The M18 is a directional above-ground mine that explodes when detonated by a firing device (M51) or a tripwire. Like a shotgun, it fires steel balls in a 60-degree arc. For rules, see page 69 of the Player’s Manual. The distinctive curved shape and folding legs have been copied by many other countries who use similar mines. The mine comes in a set with 30 meters of copper wire, tripwire, test set, and the M51 firing device (aka “clacker”)." compset="Heavy">
