  <thing id="wpT2KPFMMine" name="PFM Scatterable Mine" description="The PFM is a Soviet scatterable anti-personnel mine that can be deployed from mortars, helicopters, and aircraft in large numbers. They glide to the ground without exploding and explode later on contact. This mine is available in two types – one that dissolves itself within two days and another that is more permanent. The two types may be used separately or in the same munitions package with 36–72 mines per container. Either is detonated with as little as 5 kg of pressure, and the mine is designed to maim rather than kill." compset="Heavy">
